- [ ] render_range() includes overscan
- [ ] HeightCache with LRU eviction","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-01T03:20:38.889253250Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-02T00:25:39.763813687Z","closed_at":"2026-02-02T00:25:39.763786236Z","close_reason":"Verified complete: Virtualized<T> container fully implemented with all acceptance criteria met. 13 tests passing.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3j8t","depends_on_id":"bd-3t87","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-03T14:32:18Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
